These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-1::.
There 7 different types of food: cherry, artichoke, lemon, peach, peas, grapefruit, cauliflower
There are 7 different nationalities: british, nigerian, italian, indian, chinese, australian, polish
 1. the person eating lemon is on the far left##1
 2. the person eating peach is not the australian##6
 3. the british is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
 4. the polish is somewhere to the right of the chinese##5
 5. the person eating peas is on the left or right of the person eating cauliflower##3
 6. the british is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
 7. the person eating grapefruit is somewhere between the person eating artichoke and the nigerian##7
 8. the nigerian is on the left of the polish##1
 9. the indian is somewhere between the person eating peas and the italian##7
10. the italian is on the left or right of the british##3
11. the chinese is on the far left##1
12. the person eating peach is somewhere to the left of the polish##5
13. the person eating peach is somewhere to the right of the person eating grapefruit##5
14. the person eating cauliflower is somewhere to the right of the person eating peas##5
15. the person eating peas is the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5     |     6     |    7    |
| Food          | lemon    | cherry    | artichoke | grapefruit | peach | peas    | cauliflower |
| Nationality   | chinese | british | italian  | australian   | indian    | nigerian | polish |

