.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-2::.
There 7 different types of food: mango, raspberry, watermelon, carrot, eggplant, kale, asparagus
The people have 7 different hobbies: reading, baking, woodworking, collecting, writing, drawing, filmmaking
 1. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere between the person eating asparagus and the person eating raspberry##7
 2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person eating carrot##1
 3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person eating kale##1
 5. the person eating mango is somewhere between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person who's hobby is baking##7
 6. the person eating kale is somewhere between the person eating carrot and the person who's hobby is woodworking##7
 7. the person eating eggplant is somewhere between the person eating carrot and the person eating raspberry##7
 8. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 9. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the left of the person eating eggplant##5
10. the person eating eggplant is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
11. the person who's hobby is drawing is not the person eating asparagus##6
12. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
13. the person who's hobby is writing is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person eating carrot##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |       5       |      6      |    7    |
| Food    | asparagus  | watermelon | kale | carrot | mango     | eggplant | raspberry  |
| Hobby   | woodworking | drawing | baking  | filmmaking  | writing | collecting      | reading |

