 8. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3
 9. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere between the fan of indie and the fan of classical##7
10. the fan of house is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
11. the person who's hobby is drawing is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is drawing is not the fan of dubstep##6
13. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's hobby is drawing##7
14. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3
15. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3
16. the person who's hobby is drawing is not the fan of gospel##6
17. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the fan of folk##3
18. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
